</header>

<div class="body" id="fhbody-174804674">
	
		
	

	
		
		<div id="text-174804674" class="p">
			
		 	
				<a href="/~bobdevine">bobdevine</a> writes: <i> The Linux operating system has reached a notable milestone in desktop market share, according to the latest data from StatCounter. As of July 2024, Linux has <a href="https://ostechnix.com/linux-market-share-july-2024-report/">achieved a 4.45% market share</a> for desktop operating systems worldwide. While this percentage might seem small to those unfamiliar with the operating system landscape, it represents a significant milestone for Linux and its dedicated community. What makes this achievement even more thrilling is the upward trajectory of Linux's adoption rate.</i><br>
		 	
		</div>

		

		

		
			
		
	</div>
